<br>
There is ALWAYS a single most important one.<br>
<br>
I chose to be a shadowknight because of the combat potential, I work fairly well with my chosen profession's role, it comes fairly naturally. <br>
<br>
I chose to be human so that I would not get stuck in hallways as an ogre or troll.  I miss having the ability to slam things though.<br>
<br>
I chose the combination, feeling I can role play well with it.<br>
